  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So actually they worked with my father's money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then once the livestock grew up, then, then it belonged to my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they made their profit, and then my father would resell it, export it also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father exported to Israel also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And matter of fact, matter of fact, my father gave some livestock as gifts to Israel to a kibbutz in Israel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't remember now the name, but I think it was a kibbutz where Hannah Senesh wanted to go, I think.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You heard of Hannah Senesh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was before she escaped from Hungary and got captured.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was done in probably in 1938, 1938 or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time in Israel, they had problems with the British.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this was part of my father's business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] doing anything besides this, which-- he was what you would call, like, an entrepreneur.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He made a lot of money, but if somebody would come in and would offer him a apartment building, a hundred-unit apartment building for a good price, then he would buy it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, ant that's how I could describe him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very creative person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But he also took a lot of chances in, in-- he never lost his money, but he took a lot of chances in his business dealings.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was under tremendous pressure, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in-- I could see.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
